name: Cohen Bow Set
description:
Start your Phunkie Punkies hair bow collection with this beautiful set. Sweet aqua bow complements a black bow with white polka dots. Studded in crystals, it's perfect for dress parties as well as the playground!

Includes one snap-on hair clip. Order headband separately.

Bows interchange with all Phunkie Punkies bows, crystals, and accessories, as well as all Phunkie Punkies headbands and clips!
